    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of large, evergreen hemlock native to the west coast of North America, from Alaska to California. It is distinguished by slightly pendulous branchlet tips.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
